<L>__{interior tangiers casino day}
<A>__{extreme close up of a slot machine. four reels with sevens across. suddenly, the power goes out. lights die down.. machine 'waaaooows' down to a dead stop. security guards, on their hands and knees, are pulling the plugs on the three giant $15,000 progressive machines, as ace talks to don ward.}
